{"tid":1176150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港航客機飛日本成田機場　3日遺失6零件  懷疑飛行途中跌落","createTime":"2019-05-29T04:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T06:20:22.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28e77a22a92d8c5d430bac501c9841b580397096","tid":1176150,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:18:31.000Z","msg":"日本傳媒報道，抵達日本東京成田機場的多架香港航空客機，近日接連發現有零件遺失，數量達6件。成田機場一度封鎖跑道搜索但無發現，相信零件在客機飛行途中跌落。香港航空表示正調查事件原因。<br />\n<br />\n日本國土交通省成田機場事務所表示，於周日（26日）至周二（28日）由香港飛抵成田機場的數架香港航空客機，於降落後均發現有零件遺失，包括燈罩和螺絲等。成田機場事後封鎖跑道並派人檢查，惟找不到任何客機零件。<br />\n<br />\n關閉跑道搜索期間，令其他航班出現延誤。成田機場表示，同一間航空公司的客機機身於短時間相繼有零件脫落，情況十分罕見。香港航空正了解事故原因。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/bkn-20190528233552457-0528_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402882b04ff98348015030e771c72b98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190528%2Fbkn-20190528233552457-0528_00822_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D402882b04ff98348015030e771c72b98&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=236c8d49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/bkn-20190528233552457-0528_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402882b04ff98348015030e771c72b98</a>"},{"pid":"47619a198e8cc721c1238bc66d04556c3c0551d3","tid":1176150,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:20:07.000Z","msg":"會唔會空中解體"},{"pid":"0fd72ec91bf5dc77a26f64b13056c950cad5685d","tid":1176150,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"運房局指定回應，已要求民航處嚴肅跟進調查，確保飛行安全。 (設計對白)"},{"pid":"7d8285e838928991814e3e3184b03dfcfe45b852","tid":1176150,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"只要有一百蚊機票，窮遊港豬都會衝上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468264867b5422f2fd6aca2ad241f262d1b37dec","tid":1176150,"uid":121085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:25:19.000Z","msg":"支那公司<br />\n唔使錢都唔坐"},{"pid":"b013cd40ad8b64641d13d43db2030a8e837fb842","tid":1176150,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"俾狗坐<br />\n解體都唔撚緊要喇"}]}